OL,13,Gyou how it came to be, and walk you
OL,14,Gthrough the electronic, mechanical,
OL,15,Gand visual design for 2024 and 2026
OL,16,Gand the reasoning behind the various
OL,17,Gdecisions we had to make along the
OL,18,Gway. We'll go through the schematic,
OL,19,Glayout, and part selection, and
OL,20,Ghopefully some of the weirder
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
